reviewText:
Edenquest: Sandra Taylor is about one hour long and the video was shot in Hawaii. Basically you have six topless models posing around the islands. There is no nudity and some of the models look like they have Brest implants. The models are:

Jennifer Lavoie from New Hampshire (Playboy August 1993)
Michelle Meyer
Chloe Jones from Texas (Penthouse Pet of the Month April 1998)
Tracy Dali from California
Kristen Williams from Texas
Lucinda Lewis from South Carolina

The seven ladies in this video are all sexy and beautiful. Since I am a die hard believer that nudity means no clothes and the ladies were topless and not nude as the back of the cover says, I can only give
Edenquest: Sandra Taylor a C.
